metadata.name: Invisiape #0001
metadata.description: INVISIAPES is a community driven collection of 2666 randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain. Our goal is to build the biggest group of apes in the Metaverse. For an accessible price of 0.02 ETH you receive 1 IAPE NFT that provides you not only an awesome PFP and a lifelong frendship with other invisible apes, but a ticket to our IRL events, Invasions, Exclusive Merch, Comic Books, and our Token.
